title: Do not send Z value through proj4
message:
Do not send Z value through proj4

It is too easy that the input Z value is referenced differently than
expected by proj4.

In this case the result will be totally off, so we are safer by just
keeping them untouched and let the user do his own correction
consciously.

title: changed URL to submodule repositories
message:
changed URL to submodule repositories

Using public https:// instead of private git@ enables everyone to clone --recursive / submodule update. Even if they have configured a public key for github but don't have that key registered to the submodules.
Previously, "git submodule update" would try to authenticate with my public key and deny access.

title: Introduce "locate current feature" & refactoring
message:
Introduce "locate current feature" & refactoring

Introduces a new button in the feature form that zooms and pans to the current
item. With a long press it will follow the current item.

This further introduces a new central access point for map settings available
to QML. This is still based on QgsMapCanvas as a bridge to modify the
QgsMapSettings but it is planned to make this the central hub and controller of
all map settings modifications.
